title: Matt Kenseth wins pole for Bank of America 500 at Charlotte
text: Matt Kenseth wins pole for Bank of America 500 at Charlotte Friday, 9 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) Matt Kenseth is fastest in Thursday qualifying for Saturday night's first race in the Contender Round of the Chase for the Sprint Cup, earning his fourth pole of the season and the 17th of his career.
